{
  "entries": [
    {
      "type": "Heading",
      "level": "H1",
      "title": "Audio - Example AI Provider API"
    },
    {
      "type": "Markdown",
      "contents": [
        "This example demonstrates how to use",
        "[an AI integration framework](https://example.com/framework) to synthesise speech from text",
        "and to transcribe speech back into text using",
        "[a hosted AI API](https://example.com/provider/docs).",
        "",
        "This example connects to a hosted AI service. An API",
        "key from your selected provider is required."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Markdown",
      "contents": [
        "---"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Heading",
      "level": "H2",
      "title": "Prerequisites"
    },
    {
      "type": "Markdown",
      "contents": [
        "- [Java runtime](https://example.com/java)",
        "- [Provider API key](https://example.com/provider/keys)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Heading",
      "level": "H2",
      "title": "Run the example"
    },
    {
      "type": "Markdown",
      "contents": [
        "1. Configure credentials",
        "",
        "   Store the provider API key in a local configuration file.",
        "",
        "   ```yaml",
        "   provider:",
        "     api-key: example-secret",
        "   ```"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "Command",
      "commands": [
        "./build-tool clean verify"
      ],
      "indent": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "Command",
      "commands": [
        "java \\",
        "  -jar './target/example-app-1.0.0.jar'"
      ],
      "output": {
        "caption": [
          "The program generates an audio file from text,",
          "then transcribes that file back into text."
        ]
      },
      "indent": 3
    }
  ]
}
